### ============================================
### MMOS API Example
### Artifact Management
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### ============================================
### Upload Artifact
### ============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/artifacts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MMOS

--MMOS
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="article.md"
Content-Type: text/markdown

< ./article.md

--MMOS
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

document

--MMOS
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="workspaceId"

workspace-demo

--MMOS--

###

### ============================================
### Upload Artifact for Execution
### ============================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/executions/{{executionId}}/artifacts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MMOS

--MMOS
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="thumbnail.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./thumbnail.png

--MMOS
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

image

--MMOS--

###

### ============================================
### Get Artifact Metadata
### ============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/artifacts/{{artifactId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================
### Download Artifact
### ============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/artifacts/{{artifactId}}/download
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================
### List Execution Artifacts
### ============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/executions/{{executionId}}/artifacts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================
### Delete Artifact
### ============================================

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/artifacts/{{artifactId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}